\c 25
\s Bhiridhadhi anorumbidza ukuru hwaMwari
\p
\v 1 Zvino Bhiridhadhi muShuhi wakapindura ndokuti\x + 2.11.\x*:
\p
\v 2 Utongi nekutyisa zvinaye; achiita rugare panzvimbo dzake dzakakwirira\x + 31.2. Isa. 24.21.\x*.
\v 3 Kune uwandu here\x + Isa. 40.26.\x* kumauto ake\x + 19.12.\x*? Uye ndiani kusingabudiri kwaari chiedza chake\x + Mat. 5.45. Jak. 1.17.\x*?
\v 4 Zvino munhu angava wakarurama sei kuna Mwari\x + 4.17-19. 9.2. 15.14-16.\x*? Kana wakaberekwa nemukadzi\x + 14.1.\x* angachena sei\x + 14.4.\x*?
\v 5 Tarira, kusvika kumwedzi, uye haubwinyi; nenyeredzi hadzina kuchena pameso pake.
\v 6 Zvishoma sei munhu, \add ari\add* honye\x + 35.8.\x*! Nemwanakomana wemunhu\x + 9.14.15.16.\x*, ari gonye\x + Map. 22.6.\x*!